<h2 id="readme">README</h2>

<p>We built a drug look-up tool of Food and Drug Administration approved medicines using the FDA National Drug Code Directory API. This includes:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Drug search tool</li>
  <li>Page listing for each FDA-approved medicine</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="data">Data</h2>

<p>Data used for this project:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://open.fda.gov/apis/drug/ndc/">National Drug Code Directory</a> (Food and Drug Administration)</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="kudos">Kudos</h2>

<p>Big kudos to FDA for:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Maintaining a public application programming interface of the data.</li>
</ul>

